channel.description:
[center][size=20pt][b]Project Noob Slayerz[/b][/size][/center]
Hello, welcome to my development thread. I have recently decided to start a new Dodian based server. I don't care if you think dodian sucks if you don't want to join don't post. All Spam/Flame will be reported.
Network - Noob Slayerz, Noob Slayerz 1 (etc -15) Pass: noob IP: 5.150.158.174 Port: 43594
[b]Spots Available[/b] Server Admin [2] Server Mod [3] Website/Forum Creater [1]* Forum Global Moderator [3] Hosters [2]* Idea Makers [0>] -Unlimited Server Coders [3]
* To be able to host the server you must host it on a NO-IP and must host it atleast 10/5.. Hoster will get Official Co Owner and Administrator on forums. Website/Forum maker will get In-game moderator.
[b]Website/Forum Creator[/b] - Owner Ethan
[b]Server Administrators[/b] - I Si Force I - Owner Ethan -
[b]Server Moderators[/b] - - -
[b]Forum GMODS[/b] - Owner Ethan - -
[b]Hosters[/b] - I Si Force I - TEMP -
[b]Idea Makers[/b] - Owner Ethan - - -
[b]Server Coders[/b] - Noob Slayerz - - - Once someone has made the website and or forums please PM ME so I can get the link approved. If it is SMFFOFREE it will be denied, I don't want Phpbb or mybb. I want SMF 1.4.
I will have 1 person coding at a time so when they are finished, they upload the source give it to me. Then whoever wants to code something next can.
[b].::Application::.[/b]
[code]Name: Position: MSN: (PM me it if you want) Age: Mature: Why You Want Pos.: Proof: (If Needed) Other: [/code]
Thanks,
- Noob Slayerz
